sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant YourServer as your-site.com
    participant OtherServer as api.example.com
    
    Note over Browser: User loads page from<br/>your-site.com
    
    Browser->>OtherServer: fetch('api.example.com/data')
    Note over Browser,OtherServer: Cross-Origin Request!
    
    alt Server allows CORS
        OtherServer->>Browser: Response + CORS headers
        Note right of OtherServer: Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *
        Browser->>Browser: ✓ Request successful
    else Server blocks CORS
        OtherServer->>Browser: Response without CORS headers
        Browser->>Browser: ✗ CORS Error!
        Note over Browser: Browser blocks the response
    end
